<Window xmlns="https://github.com/avaloniaui"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        x:Class="VirtTermMac.Views.AboutWindow"
        Title="About VirtTermMac"
        Width="360" Height="220"
        CanResize="false"
        WindowStartupLocation="CenterOwner">

    <DockPanel Margin="16">
        <Button DockPanel.Dock="Bottom" Content="OK" Click="OnOk"
                HorizontalAlignment="Center" IsDefault="True" Margin="0,12,0,0"/>
        <TextBlock TextAlignment="Center" TextWrapping="Wrap" VerticalAlignment="Center">
VirtTermMac

A graphical terminal client for VirtBBS,
connecting over its own TLS protocol
(internal/virtterm) instead of Telnet/SSH.

An Avalonia UI port of VirtTerm (WinForms),
for macOS/Linux/Windows.

Part of the VirtBBS project.
        </TextBlock>
    </DockPanel>

</Window>
